WEBVTT

00:01.435 --> 00:03.104
(male announcer)
IN THE CRIMINAL JUSTICE SYSTEM,

00:03.137 --> 00:05.739
SEXUALLY-BASED OFFENSES ARE
CONSIDERED ESPECIALLY HEINOUS.

00:05.773 --> 00:08.476
IN NEW YORK CITY,
THE DEDICATED DETECTIVES

00:08.509 --> 00:10.344
WHO INVESTIGATE
THESE VICIOUS FELONIES

00:10.378 --> 00:11.712
ARE MEMBERS
OF AN ELITE SQUAD

00:11.745 --> 00:13.747
KNOWN AS
THE SPECIAL VICTIMS UNIT.

00:13.781 --> 00:16.184
THESE ARE THEIR STORIES.

00:17.685 --> 00:21.055
[prisoners yelling]
DO IT! DO IT! DO IT!

00:21.089 --> 00:23.191
I LOVE COUGARS.
OHH...

00:25.093 --> 00:27.528
(Cragen)
WELL THIS SHOULD WIND DOWN
IN ANOTHER WEEK OR TWO.

00:27.561 --> 00:29.397
SEPTEMBER IS HELL.

00:29.430 --> 00:30.631
(Greylek)
WHY IS THAT?

00:30.664 --> 00:33.101
(Cragen)
GET ABUSED
AT SUMMER CAMP AND NOBODY TELLS

00:33.134 --> 00:34.435
UNTIL THEY GET BACK HOME.

00:34.468 --> 00:36.537
GREEK WEEK PLUS ALCOHOL

00:36.570 --> 00:38.439
EQUALS RAPE
IN THE FIRST DEGREE.

00:38.472 --> 00:40.308
AND THERE'S A SPIKE
IN D.V. CALLS BECAUSE

00:40.341 --> 00:42.076
ALL THE KIDS ARE BACK
IN SCHOOL.

00:42.110 --> 00:43.711
WHERE SHOULD I
START?

00:43.744 --> 00:45.079
LISTEN, UH...

00:45.113 --> 00:46.347
WE'RE JUST GOING
TO BE SIFTING

00:46.380 --> 00:48.582
THROUGH STATEMENTS,
CORROBORATING ALIBIS.

00:48.616 --> 00:50.418
WE GET SOMETHING CONCRETE,
WE'LL GIVE YOU A CALL.

00:50.451 --> 00:52.120
I'VE HEARD THAT BEFORE.

00:52.153 --> 00:54.155
NO ONE IS DELIBERATELY
KEEPING YOU

00:54.188 --> 00:55.389
OUT OF THE LOOP,
MS. GREYLEK.

00:55.423 --> 00:56.524
I'M SURE
IT'S AN OVERSIGHT

00:56.557 --> 00:58.092
BUT JUST SO
WE'RE CLEAR,

00:58.126 --> 00:59.193
I'LL BE SHOWING UP
AT CRIME SCENES

00:59.227 --> 01:00.528
AND SITTING IN
ON INTERVIEWS FROM NOW ON.

01:00.561 --> 01:02.096
THAT WON'T LAST.

01:02.130 --> 01:03.297
LOOK CAPTAIN, I'M COMMITTING
TO DOING THIS JOB

01:03.331 --> 01:04.432
AND DOING IT WELL.

01:04.465 --> 01:05.799
AND I'VE HEARD
THAT BEFORE.

01:07.201 --> 01:08.536
TOLD YOU I
DIDN'T TOUCH THE WHORE!

01:08.569 --> 01:09.837
YOU'RE WIFE'S
SITTING NEXT DOOR

01:09.870 --> 01:11.372
LOOKING LIKE SHE
WENT A ROUND WITH TYSON.

01:11.405 --> 01:12.540
WHAT CAME FIRST,
FRANK?

01:12.573 --> 01:14.208
THE ASS-WHIPPING
OR THE RAPE?

01:14.242 --> 01:15.409
WHAT'D SHE DO,
BURN YOUR DINNER?

01:15.443 --> 01:16.810
THE BITCH SAY
I RAPED HER?

01:16.844 --> 01:19.247
LISA HAS
VAGINAL TEARING.

01:19.280 --> 01:20.548
YOU FORCED HER
TO HAVE SEX.

01:20.581 --> 01:21.882
THAT'S A QUARTER BID
MINIMUM.

01:21.915 --> 01:23.884
AND TRUST ME, YOU'RE GONNA
BE FEELING QUITE PETITE

01:23.917 --> 01:25.619
NEXT TO THE MUSCLE MASS
UPSTATE.

01:25.653 --> 01:28.122
THAT DOESN'T SCARE ME.
"SWEET MEAT."

01:28.156 --> 01:29.390
THAT'S WHAT
THEY'RE GONNA SAY

01:29.423 --> 01:30.824
WHEN THEY REACH FOR YOU
IN THE DARK.

01:39.633 --> 01:42.436
LISA DEERING
IS IN INTERVIEW "B"

01:42.470 --> 01:43.471
IF YOU'D LIKE TO SIT IN.

01:43.504 --> 01:46.140
THERE BETTER NOT BE
A SINGLE MARK ON THE SUSPECT

01:46.174 --> 01:47.908
WHEN HE'S TRANSFERRED
TO THE TOMBS, CAPTAIN.

01:47.941 --> 01:49.910
HE'S NOT GOING ANYWHERE
UNLESS WE GET A CONFESSION.

01:49.943 --> 01:51.512
WHY NOT?

01:51.545 --> 01:53.314
MY HUSBAND DIDN'T HURT ME.

01:53.347 --> 01:55.816
SO THE KNOCKS TO YOUR NOGGIN
WERE JUST LOVE TAPS?

01:55.849 --> 01:57.218
NOTHING HAPPENED.

01:57.251 --> 01:58.419
MRS. DEERING...

01:58.452 --> 02:00.154
TESTIFYING
AGAINST YOUR HUSBAND

02:00.188 --> 02:01.589
IS THE ONLY WAY
TO STOP HIM.

02:01.622 --> 02:03.857
YOU DON'T KNOW FRANK.

02:03.891 --> 02:05.193
AND I NEED HIM.

02:05.226 --> 02:07.328
LISA, HE'S ESCALATING.

02:07.361 --> 02:09.563
LAST TIME YOU WERE HERE,
YOU NEEDED 30 STITCHES.

02:09.597 --> 02:11.765
I FELL DOWN THE STAIRS.

02:11.799 --> 02:12.800
CAN I GO?

02:12.833 --> 02:13.834
IF YOU LEAVE NOW,

02:13.867 --> 02:15.169
THE NEXT TIME I SEE YOU,

02:15.203 --> 02:16.537
YOU'LL BE IN THE MORGUE.

02:19.640 --> 02:21.175
THE E.R. AT ST. LUKE'S
HAS A THREE-YEAR-OLD

02:21.209 --> 02:22.710
WITH A SUSPICIOUS FRACTURE.

02:22.743 --> 02:24.512
I'LL RIDE ALONG
WITH YOU.

02:24.545 --> 02:26.447
UH, MAY BE NOTHIN'.

02:26.480 --> 02:28.582
WHAT ARE THE ODDS?

02:28.616 --> 02:29.717
THIS KID SAYS
HE'S GOT INFORMATION

02:29.750 --> 02:30.751
ABOUT A SEXUAL ASSAULT.

02:30.784 --> 02:31.785
WHERE DO YOU WANT HIM?

02:31.819 --> 02:34.288
MY DESK.

02:34.322 --> 02:37.157
HERE, WHY DON'T
YOU HAVE A SEAT?

02:40.761 --> 02:43.264
OKAY.

02:43.297 --> 02:45.165
RELAX, TAKE A BREATH.

02:46.834 --> 02:48.969
OKAY, WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

02:49.002 --> 02:51.339
ERIC BYERS.

02:54.275 --> 02:56.510
I DON'T, UM...

02:56.544 --> 02:58.946
I DIDN'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.

02:58.979 --> 03:00.948
AND THEN I...FIGURED--

03:00.981 --> 03:03.717
CAN YOU TELL ME
WHAT HAPPENED?

03:07.755 --> 03:09.657
[crying]
THIS--THIS IS HARD TO SAY.

03:09.690 --> 03:11.725
TAKE YOUR TIME.

03:20.368 --> 03:23.304
I LOVE HIM.

03:23.337 --> 03:26.740
BUT I KNOW IT'S WRONG.

03:26.774 --> 03:30.278
AND IT'S--IT'S GETTING HARD
NOT TO TOUCH.

03:30.311 --> 03:32.413
OKAY, ERIC,
WHO ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

03:35.015 --> 03:37.885
IT'S--IT'S CORY.

03:39.587 --> 03:42.756
HE'S MY STEPBROTHER.

04:45.052 --> 04:46.954
HOW OLD ARE YOU, ERIC?

04:50.424 --> 04:52.393
17.

04:52.426 --> 04:53.961
OKAY, I THINK WE NEED
TO CALL YOUR PARENTS.

04:53.994 --> 04:56.330
NO...NO!

04:56.364 --> 04:58.866
WHY NOT?

04:58.899 --> 05:00.968
IT'S JUST MY MOM.

05:01.001 --> 05:02.035
DAD LEFT US.

05:02.069 --> 05:04.738
HER NEW HUSBAND
DOESN'T LIKE ME.

05:04.772 --> 05:05.906
WELL, I THINK--

05:05.939 --> 05:07.107
I THINK SHE NEEDS
TO KNOW WHERE YOU ARE.

05:07.140 --> 05:10.411
THIS WILL KILL HER.

05:10.444 --> 05:13.547
BESIDES, I--I HAVEN'T...

05:13.581 --> 05:16.384
DONE ANYTHING WRONG.

05:16.417 --> 05:18.919
AT LEAST--
AT LEAST I DON'T THINK.

05:18.952 --> 05:19.920
THINK.

05:19.953 --> 05:22.456
I'VE BEEN DRINKING
A LOT.

05:22.490 --> 05:24.024
BLACKING OUT.

05:27.094 --> 05:28.829
I--I JUST--
I JUST WANT--

05:28.862 --> 05:31.999
I JUST WANT THE PICTURES
IN MY HEAD TO STOP.

05:32.032 --> 05:35.436
OKAY, WHY DON'T--
WHY DON'T YOU HAVE A SEAT?

05:35.469 --> 05:37.438
OKAY?
JUST SIT BACK DOWN.

05:46.447 --> 05:48.616
SO WHAT DO YOU
THINK ABOUT?

05:54.755 --> 05:59.059
IF I TELL YOU,
YOU'LL HATE ME.

05:59.092 --> 06:00.894
EVERYBODY WILL.

06:05.433 --> 06:08.101
IS THERE A REHAB
I CAN GO TO?

06:08.135 --> 06:12.440
REHAB IS FOR PEOPLE
WITH ADDICTIONS.

06:14.174 --> 06:16.777
SURE FEELS LIKE
I HAVE ONE.

06:16.810 --> 06:19.713
I CAN'T SLEEP.

06:19.747 --> 06:22.750
I CAN'T...THINK ABOUT
ANYTHING ELSE.

06:25.586 --> 06:28.622
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO DO?

06:47.575 --> 06:50.744
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

06:50.778 --> 06:53.481
I'VE NEVER HAD A PEDOPHILE
TURN HIMSELF IN BEFORE.

06:53.514 --> 06:55.215
HIS MOTHER JUST REMARRIED.

06:55.248 --> 06:57.818
COULD HE BE MAKING IT UP
TO GET SOME ATTENTION?

06:57.851 --> 07:01.021
WHO WOULD INVENT
SOMETHING LIKE THAT?

07:01.054 --> 07:02.456
I MEAN, THE DRINKING

07:02.490 --> 07:04.191
AND THE WAY HE
CARESSED THAT PHOTO

07:04.224 --> 07:05.559
SAYS HE'S A PEDOPHILE.

07:05.593 --> 07:06.627
HE'S ALSO A MINOR,
OLIVIA.

07:06.660 --> 07:08.195
WHO'S OVER 16,

07:08.228 --> 07:09.697
AND WE DON'T
NEED A PARENT PRESENT

07:09.730 --> 07:10.764
TO QUESTION HIM.

07:10.798 --> 07:13.133
THE KID HAS ONLY ADMITTED
TO THINKING BAD THOUGHTS,

07:13.166 --> 07:14.234
AND THAT'S NOT A CRIME.

07:14.267 --> 07:15.235
IT IS IF HE ACTED ON IT.

07:15.268 --> 07:18.939
WHAT IF HE HASN'T?

07:18.972 --> 07:21.509
THEN I WILL STOP HIM,
IF I CAN.

07:27.280 --> 07:28.749
[knock on door]

07:31.752 --> 07:33.020
DANA KELLEY?

07:33.053 --> 07:35.756
WHAT'S WRONG?
WHO'S HURT?

07:35.789 --> 07:36.990
I'M DETECTIVE OLIVIA BENSON.

07:37.024 --> 07:38.125
CAN WE TALK INSIDE?

07:40.293 --> 07:42.496
UM, YES, OF COURSE.

07:42.530 --> 07:45.599
[cartoons on TV]

07:45.633 --> 07:46.700
[door closes]

07:46.734 --> 07:48.602
UH, WHAT'S THIS ABOUT?

07:48.636 --> 07:50.904
YOUR STEPSON, CORY.

07:50.938 --> 07:52.840
HAVE YOU NOTICED ANY CHANGES
IN HIS BEHAVIOR LATELY?

07:52.873 --> 07:54.508
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
LIKE WHAT?

07:54.542 --> 07:56.777
ANY SIGNS OF MOODINESS
OR TANTRUMS,

07:56.810 --> 07:58.546
NIGHTMARES,
ANYTHING LIKE THAT?

07:58.579 --> 08:00.614
NO, NO MORE THAN USUAL.

08:00.648 --> 08:01.949
HAVE YOU NOTICED ANY...
SIGNS OF HIM

08:01.982 --> 08:03.851
NOT WANTING
TO BE TOUCHED?

08:06.153 --> 08:08.622
OKAY, YOU ARE SCARING ME.
WHAT THE HELL IS GOING ON?

08:08.656 --> 08:11.158
PLEASE JUST ANSWER
MY QUESTIONS IF YOU WOULD.

08:11.191 --> 08:12.192
IS CORY
ENROLLED IN SCHOOL?

08:12.225 --> 08:13.627
YES--KINDERGARTEN.

08:13.661 --> 08:14.928
HAVE YOU HEARD ANYTHING
FROM THE TEACHERS--

08:14.962 --> 08:15.929
ANY PROBLEMS THERE?

08:15.963 --> 08:17.297
IS THAT WHAT
THIS IS ABOUT?

08:17.330 --> 08:19.967
THEY COMPLETELY
OVERREACTED

08:20.000 --> 08:22.002
WHEN CORY PLAYED DOCTOR
WITH A LITTLE GIRL

08:22.035 --> 08:23.571
ON THE PLAYGROUND.

08:23.604 --> 08:25.539
KIDS ARE CURIOUS.
IT'S COMPLETELY NATURAL.

08:25.573 --> 08:27.608
IT'S ACTUALLY A LITTLE
MORE SERIOUS THAN THAT.

08:27.641 --> 08:30.010
AND...SEXUAL ACTING OUT

08:30.043 --> 08:32.913
CAN...OFTEN BE
A SIGN OF ABUSE.

08:36.650 --> 08:38.018
WELL, THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

08:38.051 --> 08:40.087
WHERE'S YOUR HUSBAND NOW?

08:41.689 --> 08:43.924
MY HUSBAND IS, UM...

08:43.957 --> 08:45.993
DOWNTOWN,
PLUGGING POTHOLES.

08:46.026 --> 08:47.628
OKAY, HE'S GONNA NEED
TO MEET US AT THE HOSPITAL.

08:47.661 --> 08:49.630
UH, I DON'T--
I DON'T BELIEVE THIS.

08:49.663 --> 08:51.832
WHO--WHO WOULD MAKE
THESE ACCUSATIONS?

08:51.865 --> 08:53.667
WHO IS TELLING YOU
THESE LIES?

08:53.701 --> 08:54.868
BECAUSE THEY ARE LIES.

08:54.902 --> 08:57.605
YOUR SON...ERIC.

09:00.608 --> 09:02.075
WHY WOULD HE SAY THAT?

09:02.109 --> 09:05.746
WE BELIEVE THAT HE'S
BEEN ABUSING CORY.

09:09.049 --> 09:11.585
WELL, THAT'S NOT TRUE.

09:11.619 --> 09:13.654
THAT IS NOT TRUE.

09:13.687 --> 09:14.722
I NEED TO SEARCH HIS ROOM.

09:14.755 --> 09:15.789
NO, WELL,
YOU CAN FORGET IT.

09:15.823 --> 09:17.290
BECAUSE I...

09:17.324 --> 09:19.059
WILL NOT COOPERATE
WITH YOU

09:19.092 --> 09:21.695
UNTIL YOU CAN PROVE TO ME
THAT MY SON HAS DONE THIS.

09:21.729 --> 09:24.164
WE'RE NOT GONNA KNOW THAT
UNTIL AFTER THE MEDICAL EXAM.

09:28.636 --> 09:29.770
IS CORY ALL RIGHT?

09:29.803 --> 09:32.906
HE'S STILL
IN WITH DR. LAROM.

09:32.940 --> 09:35.643
IF I SEE ERIC AGAIN,
I'M GONNA KILL HIM.

09:35.676 --> 09:36.644
THAT'S A PROMISE.

09:36.677 --> 09:38.078
CALM DOWN, MR. KELLEY.

09:38.111 --> 09:40.681
THREATENING YOUR STEPSON
ISN'T GONNA HELP CORY.

09:40.714 --> 09:42.616
ERIC DID NOT DO THIS.
I KNOW HE DIDN'T.

09:42.650 --> 09:44.284
THEN WHY
GO TO THE POLICE?

09:44.317 --> 09:45.986
BECAUSE HE IS LOST.

09:46.019 --> 09:47.688
HIS FATHER ABANDONED HIM,

09:47.721 --> 09:48.555
AND MAYBE HE THINKS
I DID TOO.

09:48.588 --> 09:50.390
I DON'T KNOW.
YOU'RE DELUSIONAL, DANA.

09:50.423 --> 09:53.694
ONLY A TWISTED PERVERT
WOULD ADMIT TO ABUSING A CHILD.

09:53.727 --> 09:55.395
HE NEEDS OUR HELP, SEAN.

09:55.428 --> 09:58.165
YEAH, WELL, HE ISN'T
GONNA GET IT FROM ME.

09:59.166 --> 10:00.634
(woman)
DETECTIVE...

10:00.668 --> 10:03.637
THERE ARE NO OUTWARD SIGNS
OF PENETRATION.

10:03.671 --> 10:05.272
NO ANAL ABRASIONS,

10:05.305 --> 10:07.307
AND NO EVIDENCE
OF MUCOSAL TEARS.

10:07.340 --> 10:08.676
I DIDN'T FIND ANY SAP
IN HIS THROAT, EITHER.

10:08.709 --> 10:10.043
SAP?

10:10.077 --> 10:11.745
UH, SEMINAL ACID
PHOSPHATASE.

10:11.779 --> 10:13.313
OH, GOD.

10:13.346 --> 10:15.015
I HAD TO GIVE CORY
A SEDATIVE,

10:15.048 --> 10:16.984
SO HE'LL WANT TO SLEEP
WHEN YOU GET HIM HOME.

10:20.721 --> 10:22.055
I TOLD YOU ERIC
DIDN'T DO THIS.

10:22.089 --> 10:24.825
WE STILL DON'T KNOW THAT,
MRS. KELLEY.

10:24.858 --> 10:26.694
WHAT DO YOU--
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

10:26.727 --> 10:28.295
WHEN THERE IS AN ORAL
OR DIGITAL ASSAULT,

10:28.328 --> 10:31.164
IT DOESN'T LEAVE
ANY PHYSICAL MARKS.

10:33.901 --> 10:36.704
THERE'S JUST NO WAY TO TELL.

10:38.171 --> 10:39.740
I'M SORRY.

10:50.751 --> 10:52.119
HEY, HOW'D IT GO

10:52.152 --> 10:53.787
WITH THE BATTERED KID
AT ST. LUKE'S?

10:53.821 --> 10:55.355
D.C.S. PUT HIM
IN FOSTER CARE,

10:55.388 --> 10:56.356
MOTHER'S IN CUSTODY.

10:56.389 --> 10:58.225
