ERIC'S ACTED ON THEM.

11:04.164 --> 11:05.733
ONLY ONE WAY TO FIND OUT.

11:11.839 --> 11:13.774
DID YOU TALK
TO MY MOTHER?
YEAH.

11:13.807 --> 11:15.042
DOES SHE KNOW?
YEAH, SHE KNOWS.

11:15.075 --> 11:16.810
I-IS SHE COMING?

11:16.844 --> 11:18.779
